elements.name: System instrument test part two (Agilent N1914A)

embeddings.name: System instrument test part two (Agilent N1914A)

steps.name: Open METCAL Runtime and enter valid login and password for MC user
Click on the LogIn button
Add Agilent "N1914A", assert "IEEE, EPM, SCPI" and verify Asset info button disabled
Add barcode "TestBarcode" and Verify Asset Info button is enabled
Click Help button and verify help page is opened assert "System Instrument Dialog" and click ok button
Verify Channel A and Channel B barcode fields are disabled
Verify Channel C and Channel D barcode fields are disabled
Verify Power Sensors Drop Down is enabled for Chanel A and Chanel B
Verify Power Sensors Drop Down is disabled for Chanel C and Chanel D
select USB Ports check box
Verify Power Sensors Drop Down is enabled for Chanel C and Chanel D
Verify + buttons for all channels are enabled and - buttons for all channels are disabled
Verify Barcode fields for all channels are disabled and Asset Info buttons are disabled for all channels Barcode fields
Select any power sensor for Channel A and Verify Barcode field for that sensor is enabled
Enter barcode for that sensor and Verify corresponding Asset Info button is enabled
Select all available power sensors for Channel A with their barcodes and Verify power sensor dropdowns are disabled for Channel B, C and D
Delete one power sensor from Channel A by clicking minus button and Verify power sensor dropdowns are enabled for all channels
Click ok button
Verify "Agilent N1914A" is present on the instrument page
Click on the instrument and click Delete button
click Yes button on the Confirm window and verify instrument "Agilent N1914A" succesfully deleted
